org.efaps.admin.datamodel.ui

Class FieldValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.efaps.admin.datamodel.ui.FieldValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Object>, IUIValue

    public class FieldValue
extends Object
implements Comparable<Object>, IUIValue
    This class is used as the value for a field. It can be used to get the for the user interface necessary strings etc.
